query:
SELECT r.id, r.status, r.startedAt, r.finishedAt, r.errorMessage,
       l.level, l.message, l.createdAt
FROM execution_runs r
LEFT JOIN execution_logs l ON l.runId = r.id
ORDER BY r.id DESC, l.createdAt ASC
LIMIT 60;
